==Trolling Ferret Owners==

[[Image:RAGE.jpg|thumb|[[RAGE|<font color="green">>Fuck you my ferret is better than you.</font>]]]]

Trolling these stupid faggots is really easy, as they are, again, clearly diminished in mental capacity. They will [[tl;dr|go on endlessly]] about how great these little shits are, mostly as a facade, to hide the fact that they are secretly ashamed of their failure of a pet. Knowing that is half the battle. Some common ways of trolling these idiots are:
*Saying [[Asspies|pretty much anything remotely negative]].
*[[Caturday|Spamming cats]] in their faggy [[Anti-lulz|Ferret Friday]] threads on /an/ ([[Pokemon|IT'S SUPER EFFECTIVE!]])<br>
*Tell them that a cat or a dog, or even a fucking goldfish, is >9,000 times better than a shitty ferret, any day of the week.
*Also, posting pictures of [[dead]] stinkrats. For some reason these are really easy to come by.

